<item>
            <title>[LU-17528] Cleanup context_mit code</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17528</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Support for MIT Kerberos prior to 1.4 can be dropped now. So cleanup context_mit support and use standard access to security context via functions exported by the GSS API.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
